column5: Had to take these shots.  Paul and Ralphie were out front all day doing yard work and getting the boat ready for the season.  I didn't hear any more noise for quite some time and had to investigate.  This is what I saw
LMAO Roy syndrome.  I cant stop laughing.
Looks like me last week at least I made it to bed. I hope to get the boat ready next week or so. What a start to spring
Oh Joey revenge is a dish best served cold, but thanks for the laugh at Paul's expense.
I recognized the Roy pose right away Joey
I'm putting up the Christmas lights up in a basket too!
Classic oldphart pose if you ask me.   Casey and I are already hard at work perfecting the position.
:thumbsup_anim:  Why would you do that...thats so evil....hehe.
LOL.  Love it Joey!  It appears you work him too hard...I think it's time you went
Dog darn tired right out. LOL!! Great pic!!
